      "comment": "LOST YOUR MARKER (4) was well supported last time but could only manage second (19.05), beaten 4.5 lengths. Safe beginner but has a tricky box to overcome. Likely to be in the finish again. UTAH GUNN (7) is a capable type and proved too classy last time to win by 2 lengths at this track in a handy 19.00 beating Lady Elloise. Good beginner but will need a little luck early crossing from an outside draw. Has hit winning form and can go on with it. ZABDON JUSTICE (1) has mixed form recently, finishing seventh (17.10) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Can improve sharply here. JADE CLOVER (2) cannot be underestimated.",
